    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-serif mb-4">3. Custom Orders</h2>
    <p>
      Customised cakes and desserts are non-refundable once design and
      production have started.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-serif mb-4">4. Quality Concerns</h2>
    <p>
      If you experience any issue with your order, please contact us within
